rand() 

	说明：改函数从0-1中随机取一个小数

	select * from question order by rand() limit 0,4; ---> rand() 0.5 ----> 5 ----> order by 5

	+------------+-----------+---------+---------+---------+---------+--------+
	| questionId | title     | optionA | optionB | optionC | optionD | answer |
	+------------+-----------+---------+---------+---------+---------+--------+
	|         16 | 120-100=? | 110     | 20      | 12      | 1       | B      |
	|         15 | 22*4=?    | 124     | 66      | 77      | 88      | D      |
	|         10 | 6*9=?     | 123     | 54      | 67      | 68      | B      |
	|         14 | 17-9=?    | 7       | 6       | 8       | 0       | C      |
	+------------+-----------+---------+---------+---------+---------+--------+